t-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Atrik&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; :</span>&nbsp;tidak mempunyai flagel<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; font-size: 12px; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Monotrik&nbsp;:&nbsp;</span>mempunyai satu flagel pada salah satu ujungnya<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; font-size: 12px; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Lofotrik&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp;</span>mempunyai sejumlah flagel pada salah satu ujungnya<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; font-size: 12px; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 16.7pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Amfitrik&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp;</span>mempunyai sejumlah flagel pada kedua ujungnya<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; background-image: initial